</ul>

<h2>Indian-specific FAQs</h2>

<div class="faq-item"><h3>How does RazorpayX Payroll differ from Keka or greytHR?</h3><p>RazorpayX is payroll-first with banking integration; Keka and greytHR are full HRMS with payroll as one module. If your only HR pain is paying salaries correctly with TDS and PF deducted and reconciled, RazorpayX is faster and cheaper. If you need leave, performance, OKRs, attendance, hiring workflow, pick a full HRMS.</p></div>
<div class="faq-item"><h3>What does RazorpayX Payroll cost?</h3><p>Approximately ₹100 per employee per month for the standard plan, with the first few employees often free. Indian payment native, GST invoice automatic, integrated with Razorpay's payments stack for salary disbursement.</p></div>
<div class="faq-item"><h3>Does it handle PF, ESI, PT, TDS compliance?</h3><p>Yes, automatically. PF and ESI deducted, deposited via challan, ECR filed. Professional tax computed by state. TDS deducted under Section 192, Form 16 generated at year-end. The compliance pieces are handled end-to-end.</p></div>
<div class="faq-item"><h3>Can salaries be disbursed in one click?</h3><p>Yes, this is the core RazorpayX feature. Approved payroll triggers salary disbursement to all employees in one approval, including the statutory deposits (PF challan, ESI challan, TDS challan). The whole monthly cycle compresses from days to minutes.</p></div>
<div class="faq-item"><h3>Is RazorpayX Payroll suitable for a 50-person company?</h3><p>Yes, ideal range. Once you cross ~100 employees and need OKRs, performance management, hiring, and engagement, you graduate to Keka or greytHR. For pure-payroll teams under 100, RazorpayX is the cleanest.</p></div>

<h2>Final verdict</h2>
<p>For Indian startups under 100 employees that want payroll done correctly without buying a full HRMS, RazorpayX Payroll is the cleanest tool in 2026. One-click monthly close. Indian banking integration. Compliance handled end-to-end. The graduation path to Keka or greytHR is well-trodden when the team scales.</p>
